(7, 'Hand-Drawn Portfolio Website', 'Web Development', 'A creative portfolio website featuring hand-drawn aesthetics, interactive animations, and a unique sketchbook-inspired interface built with Next.js and TypeScript.', '<section class=\"project-header\">\r\nA modern portfolio website built with Next.js 14 and TypeScript, featuring a unique hand-drawn aesthetic, interactive paper-like textures, and engaging SVG animations. This project combines artistic design elements with modern web development practices to create an immersive and personal browsing experience.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<h2>Key Features:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Hand-Drawn UI Elements: Custom SVG animations that simulate real-time drawing effects<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Paper Textures: Realistic paper-like backgrounds with various styles (lined, grid, dotted)<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Interactive Components: Animated buttons, paths, and elements with natural movements<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Portfolio Showcase: Dynamic project grid with filtering and smooth transitions<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Blog System: Journal-style blog with categories and search functionality<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Contact Form: Interactive contact page with animated paper airplane effect<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Responsive Design: Sketchbook-inspired layouts that adapt to all screen sizes<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Dark Mode Prevention: Forced light mode to maintain the paper aesthetic<br><br>\r\n<h2>Technical Implementation:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Built with Next.js 14 and TypeScript for robust, type-safe development<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Styled with Tailwind CSS for custom paper-like design system<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Framer Motion for smooth, natural-feeling animations<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Custom SVG path animations for hand-drawn effects<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Client-side rendering optimizations for animation performance<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ CSS Grid and Flexbox for responsive layouts<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Custom font implementation with next/font<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Deployment configuration with Netlify for continuou