(12, 'Wisey - AI-Powered Interview Practice Platform', 'Web Development', 'An advanced interview preparation platform powered by Next.js, React, and AI technologies that offers personalized mock interviews, real-time feedback, and detailed performance analytics for job seekers.', '<section class=\"project-header\">\r\nA modern AI-powered interview preparation platform designed to help job seekers practice and improve their interview skills. Built with Next.js and React, Wisey combines cutting-edge AI voice interaction with sophisticated feedback systems to create a realistic interview simulation environment. The platform delivers personalized interview experiences and detailed performance analytics to help users excel in real interviews.\r\n<br><br>\r\n<h2>Key Features:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Interactive Voice Interviews: AI-powered voice interviews with natural conversation flow using VAPI.ai technology<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Custom Interview Generation: Personalized interview questions based on job role and technology stack<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Real-time Transcription: Live transcription of responses during the interview process<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Comprehensive Feedback System: AI-generated performance analysis with specific improvement recommendations<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Performance Scoring: Detailed scoring across multiple interview competency categories<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Tech Stack Visualization: Visual representation of technology requirements for different roles<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Interview History: Track progress and improvements across multiple practice sessions<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Responsive Design: Seamless experience across desktop and mobile devices<br><br>\r\n<h2>Technical Implementation:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Built with Next.js 15.2.3 and React 19.0.0 for server-side rendering and optimal performance<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ TypeScript for type-safe development and enhanced code quality<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Firebase Authentication and Firestore for secure user management and data storage<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ VAPI.ai SDK integration for natural voice conversation capabilities<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Google AI integration with Gemini-2.0 model for sophisticated feedback analysis<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Tailwind CSS for responsive and customizable UI components<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Server Actions for efficient backend operations<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ React Hook Form with Zod validation for robust form handling<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Dayjs for efficient date formatting and manipulation<br><br>\r\nThe platform creates a seamless and realistic interview environment where users can practice responding to industry-specific questions. The system analyzes responses across multiple dimensions including communication skills, technical knowledge, problem-solving abilities, and overall confidence. After each interview, users receive comprehensive feedback with actionable insights to improve their performance in future interviews.<br><br>\r\n<h2>Project Links:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Live Demo: <a href=\"https://wisey-prep.vercel.app/\" target=\"_blank\">Wisey Interview Platform</a><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Technologies: Next.js, React, TypeScript, Firebase, VAPI.ai, Google AI<br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Version: 1.0.0<br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Course by Javascript Mastery<br><br>\r\n<p class=\"date\">An innovative interview preparation platform that uses AI voice technology to create realistic mock interviews with detailed performance analysis and personalized improvement recommendations.</p>\r\n</section>', 'Images/projects/Screenshot 2025-03-27 014229.png', '[\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot 2025-03-27 014251.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot 2025-03-27 014312.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot 2025-03-27 014332.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot 2025-03-27 014354.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot 2025-03-27 014401.png\"]', 'Next.js 15.2.3, React 19.0.0, TypeScript, Firebase, VAPI.ai SDK, Google Gemini 2.0, Tailwind CSS, React Hook Form, Zod, Framer Motion, Dayjs', '- Implementing reliable voice conversation interfaces with natural-sounding AI responses<br>\r\n- Creating accurate real-time transcription during interview sessions<br>\r\n- Developing sophisticated analysis algorithms for detailed interview feedback<br>\r\n- Building responsive UI components that adapt across different devices and screen sizes<br>\r\n- Managing complex state between voice interactions and feedback generation<br>\r\n- Optimizing Firebase data structure for efficient retrieval of interview history<br>\r\n- Ensuring consistent voice quality and responsiveness across different network conditions<br>', '- Integrated VAPI.ai SDK with custom configurations to ensure natural conversation flow<br>\r\n- Implemented server-side Google AI processing for accurate and detailed feedback generation<br>\r\n- Created modular component architecture separating UI concerns from interview logic<br>\r\n- Developed custom Firebase hooks for optimized data fetching and state management<br>\r\n- Built responsive interview cards with dynamic tech stack visualization<br>\r\n- Applied Tailwind CSS with custom animations for smooth, consistent UI experience<br>\r\n- Designed scalable feedback analysis system with categorized scoring methodology<br>\r\n- Established robust authentication flow with session management for secure user experiences<br>', '2025-03-17', '2025-03-27 02:58:29', '2025-05-31 04:17:10', 'Completed', '2025-03-29', NULL, '[]'),
(13, 'Ability System Prototype in Godot', 'Game Development', 'A focused technical demo built with Godot Engine that implements a robust ability system with cooldown management and animation integration for 2D character gameplay.', '<section class=\"project-header\"><br>A technical demonstration developed using the Godot Engine, focusing specifically on implementing an ability system with cooldown management. This prototype explores the implementation of character abilities in a 2D environment with proper animation handling and physics integration.<br><br><br>\r\n<h2>Key Features:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Ability System: Implementation of four distinct abilities with independent cooldown tracking<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ UI Feedback: Visual cooldown indicators showing ability availability status<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Animation Integration: Seamless transition between character movement and ability animations<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Physics-Based Dash: Custom dash mechanic with collision detection and proper animation timing<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Character Controller: Basic 2D platformer movement serving as foundation for ability implementation<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Visual Positioning: Dynamic sprite offset system to properly align ability animations<br><br>\r\n<h2>Technical Implementation:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Built with Godot Engine 4.4<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Frame-specific animation control for abilities<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Modular ability framework for easy expansion<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Physics-integrated movement with collision detection<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ State-based character controller<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ UI integration with gameplay systems<br><br>\r\nThis prototype demonstrates specific technical skills in game development, particularly focused on ability implementation, animation handling, and user interface feedback systems. The project serves as a practical exploration of these game mechanics rather than a complete game.<br><br>\r\n<h2>Project Links:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Engine: <a href=\"https://godotengine.org\">Godot 4.4</a><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Status: Completed Technical Demonstration<br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Platform: PC (Windows/Linux)<br><br>\r\n<p class=\"date\">This project was created as a focused technical exercise to explore ability implementation in Godot Engine.</p>', 'Images/projects/250401_12h11m02s_screenshot.png', '[\"Images\\/gallery\\/250401_12h12m36s_screenshot.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/250401_12h12m49s_screenshot.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/250401_12h13m06s_screenshot.png\"]', 'Godot Engine, GDScript', '- Implementing ability cooldown system with visual feedback<br>\r\n- Integrating different-sized ability animations with character movement<br>\r\n- Handling collision detection during dash ability movement<br>\r\n- Managing animation transitions between abilities and normal movement<br>\r\n- Synchronizing ability animation timing with movement effects<br>\r\n- Creating responsive UI elements for ability status indication<br>', '- Developed modular ability system with independent cooldown tracking for each ability<br>\r\n- Implemented dynamic sprite offset system to properly position different ability animations<br>\r\n- Created physics-based dash with proper collision detection and frame-specific movement<br>\r\n- Built state management system to handle transitions between movement and ability states<br>\r\n- Synchronized animation frames with movement mechanics for the dash ability<br>\r\n- Designed responsive UI with TextureProgress nodes to display cooldown status<br>', '2025-04-01', '2025-04-01 12:17:16', '2025-04-01 12:17:16', 'Completed', '2025-04-01', NULL, '[\"EH-XeFPuvI4\"]'),
(14, 'RedM Stable NPC System', 'Game Development', 'A comprehensive stable management system for RedM servers featuring interactive NPCs, horse purchasing, and a complete user interface with database integration.', '<section class=\"project-header\"><br>A technical demonstration developed using the RedM framework for FiveM, focusing specifically on implementing an interactive stable system with NPC management. This script creates immersive stable interactions in the Red Dead Redemption 2 multiplayer environment with proper animation handling and entity integration.<br><br><br>\r\n<h2>Key Features:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ NPC System: Implementation of stable attendants with automatic spawning, error handling, and fallback models<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ UI Feedback: Clean user interface for browsing and purchasing horses with visual stat indicators<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Animation Integration: Seamless transition between NPC idle animations and player interactions<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Database-Integrated: Complete database storage system for tracking player-owned horses<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Multiple Payment Methods: Support for both cash and bank account transactions<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Debug Toolkit: Comprehensive troubleshooting commands for server administrators<br><br>\r\n<h2>Technical Implementation:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Built with Lua for RedM platform<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Entity persistence with regular validity checks and respawning<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Modular config-based framework for easy expansion<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ NUI-based UI system with responsive design<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ State-based interaction controller<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Multi-stable support with location-specific configurations<br><br>\r\nThis script demonstrates specific technical skills in game development, particularly focused on entity management, animation handling, and user interface integration. The project serves as a practical solution for RedM roleplay servers requiring a stable system with realistic interactions.<br><br>\r\n<h2>Project Links:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Framework: <a href=\"https://redm.net/\">RedM</a><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Status: Completed and Production-Ready<br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Platform: RedM Servers (Windows/Linux)<br><br>\r\n<p class=\"date\">This project was created as a practical solution for RedM roleplay servers, demonstrating advanced entity management techniques and database integration.</p>\r\n</section>', 'Images/projects/REDM Thumbnail 2.png', '[\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot_2025-04-08-09-27-46-126_com.miui.videoplayer-edit.jpg\"]', 'RedM Framework, Lua Language, MySQL, NUI System, RedM Native Functions, HTML/CSS/JS (for UI)', '- Implementing stable NPC persistence with reliable spawning and respawning<br>\r\n- Managing multiple stable locations with unique configurations<br>\r\n- Integrating database storage for horse ownership and transactions<br>\r\n- Handling concurrent player interactions with the stable system<br>\r\n- Creating responsive UI elements that work across different screen resolutions<br>\r\n- Synchronizing server-side and client-side horse ownership states<br>', '- Developed robust NPC management system with automatic respawning and model fallbacks<br>\r\n- Implemented modular configuration system for easy addition of new stable locations<br>\r\n- Created efficient database structure with both MySQL and in-memory storage options<br>\r\n- Built state management system to handle player interactions and prevent conflicts<br>\r\n- Designed responsive NUI interface with clean separation of concerns<br>\r\n- Synchronized horse ownership data using reliable server-client events<br>', '2025-04-07', '2025-04-08 08:36:19', '2025-04-09 09:04:39', 'In Development', NULL, NULL, '[\"zBTXrdnxp5c\"]'),
(15, 'RedM Admin Teleport System', 'Game Development / Server Administration Tools', 'A secure and optimized admin teleportation system for RedM servers featuring a graphical user interface, predefined locations, and comprehensive admin-only commands for efficient server management.', '<section class=\"project-header\"><br>A technical demonstration developed for the RedM framework, focusing specifically on implementing a secure and efficient admin teleportation system. This script provides server administrators with essential tools for world navigation while maintaining strict access control and server security.<br><br><br>\r\n<h2>Key Features:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Admin Control System: Secure permission-based access control for all teleport commands<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ UI Integration: Clean graphical interface accessible via hotkey or command<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Position Management: Advanced position marking and recall system<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Coordinate Precision: Support for exact coordinate teleportation with both client and server-side options<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Location Presets: Predefined location system for quick navigation<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Optimized Performance: Lightweight implementation with minimal resource usage<br><br>\r\n<h2>Technical Implementation:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Built with Lua for RedM platform<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Server-side permission validation<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ NUI-based menu system<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Configurable keybinding system<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Modular command structure<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Comprehensive error handling<br><br>\r\nThis script demonstrates specific technical skills in server administration tool development, particularly focused on security, user interface design, and efficient command handling. The project serves as a practical solution for RedM server administrators requiring reliable teleportation tools.<br><br>\r\n<h2>Project Links:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Framework: <a href=\"https://redm.net/\">RedM</a><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Status: Production-Ready (Version 2.2.0)<br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Platform: RedM Servers (Windows/Linux)<br><br>\r\n<p class=\"date\">This project was created as an essential administration tool for RedM servers, emphasizing security and ease of use.</p>\r\n</section>', 'Images/projects/RedM Thumbnail 1.png', '[\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot_2025-04-08-09-50-57-131_com.miui.videoplayer-edit.jpg\"]', 'Lua Language, RedM Framework, NUI (Native UI) System, HTML/CSS/JavaScript, RedM Native Functions, ACE Permission System', '- Implementing secure admin-only access control<br>\r\n- Creating a responsive and intuitive UI for quick navigation<br>\r\n- Managing coordinate precision across different map regions<br>\r\n- Handling position marking and recall system reliably<br>\r\n- Ensuring compatibility with server security systems<br>\r\n- Optimizing performance for minimal resource usage<br>', '- Developed comprehensive ACE permission system integration<br>\r\n- Implemented clean NUI interface with hotkey access<br>\r\n- Created precise coordinate handling with error checking<br>\r\n- Built robust position storage and recall mechanism<br>\r\n- Integrated server-side validation for all commands<br>\r\n- Optimized code structure for minimal performance impact<br>', '2025-04-07', '2025-04-08 09:08:17', '2025-04-09 09:05:29', 'Completed', '2025-04-07', NULL, '[\"q1FbtFZfPEE\"]'),
(17, '1899RP Scripts Store - The Ultimate RedM Marketplace', 'E-Commerce / Web Development / Digital Marketplace', 'A specialized e-commerce platform for RedM scripts and modifications, featuring secure payment integration, license management, and an authentic Wild West-themed UI. This marketplace connects script developers with server owners in the Red Dead Redemption', '<section class=\"project-header\"><br>A comprehensive e-commerce platform developed for the RedM community, focusing specifically on creating a secure and optimized marketplace for Wild West roleplay scripts and modifications. This store connects talented developers with server administrators seeking high-quality content to enhance their RedM servers while providing robust license management and secure payment processing.<br><br><br>\r\n<h2>Key Features:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Payment Integration: Secure multi-gateway payment processing with Stripe and PayPal integration<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ License Management: Comprehensive KeyMaster system for secure script licensing and distribution<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ User Management: Complete authentication system with role-based access control and email verification<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Product Showcase: Detailed script listings with media galleries, feature lists, and technical specifications<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Western-Themed UI: Immersive interface designed to complement the Wild West roleplay experience<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Developer Dashboard: Comprehensive sales analytics and version management for script creators<br><br>\r\n<h2>Technical Implementation:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Frontend built with React.js and Tailwind CSS<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Node.js/Express.js backend with TypeScript<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ PostgreSQL database with TypeORM<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ JWT-based authentication system<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Stripe and PayPal payment gateway integration<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Responsive design for all device types<br><br>\r\nThis platform demonstrates advanced skills in e-commerce development, payment gateway integration, and secure user authentication. The project serves as a specialized marketplace that bridges the gap between RedM script developers and server owners seeking premium content for their roleplay communities.<br><br>\r\n<h2>Project Links:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Framework: <a href=\"https://redm.net/\">RedM</a><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Marketplace: <a href=\"https://1899rp.store\">1899RP Scripts Store</a><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Platform: Web-based (Responsive)<br><br>\r\n<p class=\"date\">This project was created as the premier marketplace for authentic Wild West roleplay experiences, emphasizing security, developer support, and immersive design.</p>\r\n</section>', 'Images/projects/Screenshot 2025-05-22 095640.png', '[\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot 2025-05-22 154319.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot 2025-05-22 154328.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot 2025-05-22 154339.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot 2025-05-22 154352.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/Screenshot 2025-05-22 154359.png\"]', 'React.js, Node.js, Express.js, TypeScript, PostgreSQL, TypeORM, JWT Authentication, Stripe API, PayPal API, Tailwind CSS, AWS S3, Axios, Formik, Framer Motion, Headless UI', '- Implementing secure payment processing with multiple gateways<br>\r\n- Creating a western-themed UI that remains functional and intuitive<br>\r\n- Developing a robust license management system for digital products<br>\r\n- Building a scalable database structure for complex e-commerce relationships<br>\r\n- Handling secure file uploads and downloads for digital products<br>\r\n- Ensuring compatibility across different payment methods and regions<br>', '- Integrated Stripe and PayPal APIs with comprehensive error handling<br>\r\n- Designed an immersive UI with Tailwind CSS and React components<br>\r\n- Built a secure KeyMaster system for license generation and validation<br>\r\n- Implemented TypeORM with PostgreSQL for efficient data relationships<br>\r\n- Created a secure file management system with access control<br>\r\n- Developed region-specific payment handling with multiple currencies<br>', '2025-04-17', '2025-05-22 09:02:01', '2025-05-22 14:44:32', 'Completed', '2025-04-18', NULL, '[]'),
(18, 'RepoDigest - Advanced Codebase Analysis CLI', 'Developer Tools / CLI Applications', 'Advanced CLI tool that transforms any codebase into intelligent, LLM-ready text digests with smart filtering, multiple output formats, and detailed analytics.', '<section class=\"project-header\"><br>\r\nA powerful command-line tool engineered to revolutionize how developers interact with codebases in the AI era. RepoDigest transforms any Git repository or local directory into comprehensive, structured digests optimized for Large Language Models while providing intelligent insights about codebase composition. This tool bridges the gap between traditional development workflows and modern AI-assisted coding practices.<br><br><br>\r\n\r\n<h2>Key Features:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Multi-Format Output: Generate digests in text, JSON, or Markdown formats optimized for different consumption methods<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Smart File Analysis: Advanced binary detection, programming language identification, and automatic encoding recognition<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Flexible Filtering: Language-specific filtering, glob pattern matching, file size limits, and directory depth controls<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Rich Analytics: Detailed statistics with language breakdowns, token estimation, and processing performance metrics<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Interactive Configuration: Guided setup mode with intuitive prompts for complex filtering scenarios<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Beautiful Terminal UI: Modern CLI interface with progress indicators, colored output, and comprehensive help<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Git Integration: Seamless remote repository support with branch selection and private repository access<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Performance Optimized: High-speed processing with parallel operations and intelligent caching mechanisms<br><br>\r\n\r\n<h2>Technical Implementation:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Built with TypeScript and modern ES modules for type safety<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Commander.js framework for robust CLI argument parsing<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Fast-glob integration for high-performance pattern matching<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Tiktoken integration for accurate LLM token estimation<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Simple-git library for reliable repository operations<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Modular architecture with clean separation of concerns<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Cross-platform compatibility (Windows, macOS, Linux)<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Comprehensive error handling and user-friendly validation<br><br>\r\n\r\nThis tool demonstrates advanced skills in CLI development, file system analysis, and developer tooling creation. RepoDigest serves as an essential bridge between traditional codebases and AI-powered development workflows, making complex repositories instantly accessible to Large Language Models while maintaining comprehensive analytical capabilities.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<h2>Project Links:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Repository: <a href=\"https://github.com/SallahBoussettah/repodigest\">GitHub Repository</a><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Platform: Cross-platform CLI (Node.js)<br><br>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"date\">This project was created to empower developers in the AI era, providing seamless integration between traditional codebases and modern language models for enhanced productivity and intelligent development workflows.</p>\r\n</section>', 'Images/projects/Screenshot 2025-07-24 170522.png', '[]', 'Node.js 18+, TypeScript 5.4.5, Commander.js 12.1.0, Fast-glob 3.3.2, Tiktoken 1.0.14, Simple-git 3.25.0, Chalk 5.3.0, Ora 8.2.0, Inquirer 12.8.0, Figlet 1.8.2, Boxen 8.0.1, Ignore 7.0.5, Mime-types 2.1.35', '- Implementing accurate binary file detection across different file types and encodings<br>\r\n- Creating a performant file traversal system that handles large repositories efficiently<br>\r\n- Developing robust pattern matching that supports complex glob expressions and edge cases<br>\r\n- Building a scalable token estimation system for accurate LLM usage planning<br>\r\n- Handling secure Git operations with authentication for private repositories<br>\r\n- Ensuring cross-platform compatibility across different operating systems and Node.js versions<br>', '- Integrated multi-layered binary detection using MIME types, file extensions, and buffer analysis<br>\r\n- Designed an optimized file processor with parallel operations and smart caching mechanisms<br>\r\n- Built a comprehensive pattern matcher using fast-glob library for high-performance filtering<br>\r\n- Implemented tiktoken integration with fallback estimation for reliable token counting<br>\r\n- Created a secure Git wrapper with token authentication and proper error handling<br>\r\n- Developed platform-agnostic code with comprehensive testing across multiple environments<br>', '2025-07-23', '2025-07-24 16:13:47', '2025-07-24 16:13:47', 'In Development', NULL, NULL, '[]'),
(19, 'ReadWise+ - AI-Powered Reading Companion', 'Mobile Application Development', 'A beautiful, feature-rich React Native mobile app that transforms how users track their reading journey, collect memorable quotes, and discover new books through AI-powered recommendations.', '<section class=\"project-header\"><br>\r\nA sophisticated mobile reading companion engineered to revolutionize personal library management and reading discovery in the digital age. ReadWise+ combines elegant design with powerful functionality to create an immersive reading experience that helps users organize their literary journey, preserve meaningful quotes, and discover their next great read through intelligent AI recommendations. This cross-platform application demonstrates advanced mobile development skills while prioritizing user privacy and offline-first functionality.<br><br><br>\r\n\r\n<h2>Key Features:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Smart Book Management: Intuitive three-shelf system (Want to Read, Reading, Finished) with seamless book organization<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Instant Book Discovery: Real-time search powered by Google Books API with rich metadata and cover images<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Quote Collection System: Capture and organize memorable passages with custom tags and timestamps<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ AI-Powered Recommendations: Personalized book suggestions using Google Gemini AI based on reading history<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Beautiful Design System: Dark and light themes with smooth animations and responsive layouts<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Privacy-First Architecture: Complete offline functionality with local data storage and no account requirements<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Cross-Platform Compatibility: Native performance on both iOS and Android devices<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Secure API Integration: Encrypted local storage for API keys with user-controlled data management<br><br>\r\n\r\n<h2>Technical Implementation:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Built with React Native and Expo SDK for cross-platform mobile development<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ TypeScript implementation ensuring type safety and maintainable code architecture<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ AsyncStorage integration for robust offline-first data persistence<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Google Books API integration for comprehensive book metadata and search capabilities<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Google Gemini AI integration for intelligent reading recommendations<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ EAS Build configuration for professional app distribution and deployment<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Modern component architecture with clean separation of concerns<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Responsive design system optimized for various screen sizes and orientations<br><br>\r\n\r\nThis project showcases advanced mobile development expertise, API integration skills, and user experience design principles. ReadWise+ serves as a comprehensive solution for modern readers, combining traditional book tracking with cutting-edge AI technology to enhance the reading experience while maintaining complete user privacy and control.<br><br>\r\n\r\n<h2>Project Links:</h2><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Repository: <a href=\"https://github.com/SallahBoussettah/readwise-mobile\">GitHub Repository</a><br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Platform: iOS & Android (React Native/Expo)<br>\r\n&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp â€¢ Live Demo: <a href=\"https://expo.dev/accounts/sato_san/projects/readwise-plus\">Expo Development Build</a><br><br>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"date\">This project was created to empower book lovers with a comprehensive digital reading companion, seamlessly blending traditional library management with modern AI-powered discovery features for an enhanced literary journey.</p>\r\n</section>', 'Images/projects/sc1.png', '[\"Images\\/gallery\\/sc2.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/sc3.png\",\"Images\\/gallery\\/sc4.png\"]', 'React Native 0.74, Expo SDK 51.0, TypeScript 5.8, AsyncStorage, Google Books API, Google Gemini AI, EAS Build, Expo Vector Icons, React Native Dotenv', '&nbsp â€¢ Implementing seamless offline-first data persistence with AsyncStorage while maintaining data integrity<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Creating responsive UI components that adapt gracefully across different screen sizes and orientations<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Integrating multiple APIs (Google Books, Gemini AI) with robust error handling and fallback mechanisms<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Developing a secure local storage system for API keys with encryption and user privacy protection<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Building smooth animations and transitions while maintaining optimal performance on lower-end devices<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Handling complex state management across multiple views without external state management libraries<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Ensuring cross-platform compatibility between iOS and Android with platform-specific optimizations<br>', '&nbsp â€¢ Implemented AsyncStorage with JSON serialization and data validation for reliable offline functionality<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Designed flexible component architecture using React Native\'s Dimensions API and responsive design patterns<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Created comprehensive error boundary system with graceful degradation and user-friendly error messages<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Developed secure key management using encrypted storage with react-native-keychain integration<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Optimized performance using React.memo, useMemo, and useCallback for efficient re-rendering<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Utilized React\'s built-in state management with custom hooks for clean, maintainable code organization<br>\r\n&nbsp â€¢ Leveraged Expo\'s cross-platform APIs and EAS Build for consistent deployment across both platforms<br>', '2025-07-28', '2025-07-28 22:40:01', '2025-07-28 22:40:01', 'In Development', NULL, NULL, '[]');
